Package: rscodeiov2
Title: A Visual Studio Code Inspired Theme for RStudio with RStudio 2025+ Support
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Md. Hasanur", "Rahman", email = "hasanurrahman.bge@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Anthony", "North", email = "anthony.jl.north@gmail.com", role = "aut", comment = "Original rscodeio package author"),
             person("Miles", "McBain", email = "miles.mcbain@gmail.com", role = "ctb"))
Description: Provides a Visual Studio Code inspired theme for RStudio IDE with 
    revolutionary support for RStudio 2025's new web-based architecture. Features 
    automatic version detection and dual theming approach: CSS-based theming for 
    modern RStudio 2025+ and QSS-based theming for legacy versions. Includes custom 
    menu styling and enhanced editor themes with VS Code-inspired color schemes.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    fs (>= 1.5.0),
    rstudioapi (>= 0.13),
    utils
SystemRequirements: RStudio (>= 1.2.0)
URL: https://github.com/hasanur-rahman079/rscodeiov2
BugReports: https://github.com/hasanur-rahman079/rscodeiov2/issues
Lifecycle: experimental
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
